sections.heading: to 40-5-26 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1985, ch. 105, § 21 and Laws 1986, ch. 47, § 25 repealed 40-5-1 to 40-5-26 NMSA 1978, as enacted and amended by Laws 1923, ch. 32, §§ 9, 11 to 14, 17 to 20, 25 and 27, Laws 1969, ch. 100, § 1, Laws 1973, ch. 103, and Laws 1977, ch. 119, § 1, relating to illegitimacy and support.
